com.collabnet.ccf.core.eis.connection
Class ConnectionPool.ConnectionInfo

java.lang.Object
  com.collabnet.ccf.core.eis.connection.ConnectionPool.ConnectionInfo
Enclosing class:
ConnectionPool<T>
private class ConnectionPool.ConnectionInfo
extends java.lang.Object

This class's objects represent a connection in the pool. It holds a reference to the Connection object for a particular system and repository. Keeps the time when this connection was used last. A boolean value to indicate whether the Connection object associated with this ConnectionInfo object is currently used or not.
